data.description: Absolutely charming house! This home has everything you desire, and it's offered at the perfect price! With immaculate curb appeal, a maintenance-free brick front, and a private privacy-fenced backyard with a covered patio, this home is an oasis of comfort. Inside, you'll fall in love with the hardwood flooring, wood-burning fireplace, planter shelves, and sky-high ceilings that create a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The Master suite is a retreat in itself, boasting a generous size and a tray ceiling, accompanied by an enormous walk-in closet. The ensuite bathroom features double vanities, a soaker tub, and a separate shower for ultimate relaxation. Plus, the two-car attached garage provides ample storage space. Conveniently located minutes from the interstate and Moody Schools, Alden Glen offers a pool, playground, and clubhouse for endless enjoyment. And rest assured, the roof, only 3 years old, was replaced in 2021, ensuring added value and peace of mind. Come see it soon!
